Package: secrpoly
Type: Package
Title: Area Search Spatially Explicit Capture-Recapture 
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2024-09-19
Description: Functions to estimate the density and size of a spatially 
  distributed animal population sampled by searching polygons or transects.
  An experimental subset of 'secr' capability.
